name: cities-towns-and-villages-incorporated-areas-indot-in-incorporated-boundaries-in-indiana-india
notes: INCORPORATED_AREAS_INDOT_IN is a polygon shapefile that contains incorporated area boundaries (Cities and Towns) in Indiana, provided by personnel of Indiana Department of Transportation (INDOT), Graphics Engineering. The data set provided by INDOT was in an ESRI shapefile format and was named "CORPLINE_INDOT_2003." INCORPORATED_AREAS_INDOT_IN is attributed with incorporated names (and) area and perimeter numbers. An updated version of this data set was provided to personnel of the IGS by INDOT personnel on September 13, 2006. The updated data set provided was in an ESRI shapefile format, and was named "GISINFO.CORPLINE.SHP." The following is excerpted from the metadata provided by INDOT, Graphics and Engineering for the source shapefile GISINFO.CORPLINE.SHP: "The polygon shapefile represents the incorporated area boundaries ( Cities and Towns) in the State of Indiana. Approximately 568 incorporated boundaries are represented within this data set."
